{
  "$id": "qa-fail",
  "type": "object",
  "required": [
    "schema",
    "task",
    "issues"
  ],
  "properties": {
    "schema": {
      "const": "qa-fail"
    },
    "task": {
      "type": "string"
    },
    "attempt": {
      "type": "integer"
    },
    "issues": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "severity": {
            "enum": [
              "High",
              "Medium",
              "Low"
            ]
          },
          "expected": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "actual": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "evidence": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": {
              "type": "string"
            }
          },
          "fix_instruction": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "file_to_modify": {
            "type": "string"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "acceptance": {
      "type": "object"
    },
    "next": {
      "type": "string"
    }
  },
  "_note": "文档形态;运行时校验为 src-tauri/src/services/nexus_verdict.rs 的必填字段轻量校验,两者须同步维护。qa-verdict 组合 id 在校验层按 schema 字段分派到 qa-pass/qa-fail。"
}